{"data":[{"id":560848969,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"381110b0801b0325bd49a69c5a28f7ac","url_token":"jin-tian-shui-dao-zhu-yi-long-liao-ma","name":"小杨同学","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-14a3c05e0d9b78b6a92f16899f91b461_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-14a3c05e0d9b78b6a92f16899f91b461_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/381110b0801b0325bd49a69c5a28f7ac","user_type":"people","headline":"你走了也罢，如此红尘","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":1,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560848969","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545893254,"updated_time":1546325921,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"comment_count":6,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"nobody","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e评论关闭，不想看杠精们强行扭曲别人意思。说我同情民科的，我不知道是脑子里有屎还是眼睛里有眼屎，反正不是什么好东西哦。我说我同情高中生，我没有为他强行辩论到底证明出了这个猜想没有，我说了，不管有没有，不希望网络暴力伤害到他，键盘侠们毕竟生活里都是一群屌丝，想发泄自己只有靠键盘。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e还有，我说数学对于我来说是噩梦，我不怕别人说什么，我是数学渣，碍你什么事了？？？吃你家米了还是喝你家水了跟自己高潮了一样兴奋。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e非要拿杀人犯来比喻，我也是服了某些人的逻辑。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我从一开始回答的初衷，先不论是否证明出这个猜想，我是说，网络暴力永远不可取。有些人以为自己的批评是好意，是拯救别人不陷入民科，好，这个我承认是对的。可一些人打着民科的旗号干着键盘侠的勾当我就呵呵了。干嘛，非要对着别人冷嘲热讽以为自己很幽默地开玩笑我可去你 的吧，怎么，不能说加油？之前这个词比你们的唾沫更有正义感。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e别在评论里阴阳怪气，我就是觉得人家厉害行吗，一群杠精，你能证明夏朝存在你好棒棒哦，我也夸你好吗，别自己强行找存在感，跟小学生一样，学大人说话，非要大声喊出来展示自己是大人。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e分割线\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e原回答\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e看了一圈，感觉知乎都变了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e首先，高中生就有想证明哥德巴赫猜想的想法，我很佩服，至少我现在都搞不懂这个猜想是什么，大概我搞懂了也不会想去证明，数学对我来说就是噩梦。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e再者，我不会去评论你是否是单纯出名而说还是真的证明出了，这是你自己的事，网络暴力永远不可取，一群人回答问题冷嘲热讽开嘴炮，嘲笑别人不自量力，殊不知是自己做不到吃不到葡萄说葡萄酸。希望各位自重，口下留情。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后，回到正题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我觉得应该会被录取的，毕竟挺伟大的。希望你以后在数学方面有所成就。加油。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"评论关闭，不想看杠精们强行扭曲别人意思。说我同情民科的，我不知道是脑子里有屎还是眼睛里有眼屎，反正不是什么好东西哦。我说我同情高中生，我没有为他强行辩论到底证明出了这个猜想没有，我说了，不管有没有，不希望网络暴力伤害到他，键盘侠们毕竟生活…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2